</div>
         <div type="apparatus">
            <p>l.1, after <foreign xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" xsl:lang="grc">ΜΑΡ</foreign>, is written over a rasura; the erased letters presumably went with line 2.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>The burial niche belongs to Marcus Aurelius Dionysios son of Antiochos son of Sopolis, the one in the vault [ . . ? .  .]</p>
         </div>
